* Iron Raptor stoped in her tracks at the sudden announcement with the 
sounds of weapon fire which followed, rolling her eyes before turning back 
to face the way that she had come. Looking past AzureBlade and Whistler with 
a sigh.
< Well...at least I'm never bord....>
Refocusing, Iron looked from Azure to Whistler. Deciding instantly what to 
do.*

" AzureBlade,go and pay our attacker(s) a visit but remember to get the 
status of the situation from the City's artificial intelligence first. 
Cyndro. That way you'll know what you're up against.  Whistler, you're with 
me."

* Turning quickly, Iron checked her gear with remarkable timing before 
starting down the dark hall at a swift jog. She would exit the City at a 
side passage that would take her almost directly upon the transmission's 
location.*
